Poland Must ‘Do Everything It Can’ to Join Euro, President Komorowski Says

-- B y   D o r o t a   B a r t y z e l
-- 
2011-09-08T05:51:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/poland-must-do-everything-it-can-to-join-euro-president-komorowski-says.html
Poland must “do everything it can”
to adopt the euro “as quickly as possible” as the European
Union deepens cooperation among users of the single currency,
President  Bronislaw Komorowski  said today in an interview with
Radio Tok FM.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dorota Bartyzel in Warsaw at 
